Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.94,0:02:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十幕\N爱德蒙的信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您没睡过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有体力 我有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但您看来不像是没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佣人们似乎也都放假了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能让她一个人留在这个家里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.53,0:03:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 弗朗兹先生也说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚并不是给对方幸福的唯一途径
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我考虑过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在最需要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以自己的立场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克西米利安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.57,0:03:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜小姐虽然沉睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想她现在一定不安得想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要在她醒来的时候陪在她身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天我下了决心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要带她去我家乡疗养
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能让她再遭遇痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检察官大人 我有话想…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我听着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要敢将我女儿带离这房间一步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就将你视同诱拐犯处理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是恐吓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 今天在这里发生的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你何干
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝子爵 你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我直言 检察官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的家人被什么人盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至连我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到我们周围的可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.24,0:04:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个令人厌恶的伪伯爵了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 这些都是我的家事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不允许外人插手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现将关于基督山伯爵的调查报告发送给您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs22}La maison Morrel et fils：「莫雷尔父子公司」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走访首席检查官大人所指定地点的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然发现一位老神甫也在沿大致相同的路线调查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这三个月内 多次到访此地区
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.25,0:05:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神甫似乎在收集镇上一名死于贫困的老人的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老人的名字是路易·唐泰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为弄清这位老神甫的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及其与基督山伯爵的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正准备前往路易·唐泰斯生前住所调查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老人的名字是路易·唐泰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐泰斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐泰斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 今天的才艺汇演您会来看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲告诉你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然有工作 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可您答应过我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这次一定会来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸工作很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他带走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲连这点事都教不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 爱德华也很期待这天的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没问这个 废话少说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟老师说我不参加合唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去收拾行李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葬礼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葬礼的请柬送来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承大批领地是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但很多东西都不甚了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要熟知法律
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是继承了大笔遗产的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果自己不能控制遗产税 会很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 其实我正在寻找能为我理财的合伙人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 合伙人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧仁妮小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍后能到您房间拜访吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不巧 钢琴课还没上完
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是不讨喜 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话您别说出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的未婚夫家也有不少问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是给老爷的信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙·唐泰斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}L'affaire de Janina：「约阿尼纳事件」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和您说些事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选举接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多事情都不得不处理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给父亲的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葬礼的请柬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 我刚从维尔福邸回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把瓦朗蒂娜带离那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您能帮忙说服她父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 她会有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲去请求的话 维尔福先生也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要去插手他人的家事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 因为朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你或是你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:10:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没有权利擅自插手他人的家务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您什么都不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许再管了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您为何动怒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友有困难
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道能袖手旁观吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 拜托您是我的愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 板着脸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和父亲闹了点别扭而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲认识爱德蒙·唐泰斯这个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙·唐泰斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天父亲收到的信的寄件人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎的 父亲的样子就变了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 最近似乎没睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临近大选 母亲也操劳过度了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙·唐泰斯…是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底会有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你也收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是无聊的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快离开这儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人知道我们的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:13:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到齐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的老朋友卡德鲁斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发迹了就把我和那些往事都给忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位都今非昔比 飞黄腾达了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你干的吗 卡德鲁斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种无聊事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是收请柬的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有谁知道我们的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我们之外还有谁能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.17,0:14:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙·唐泰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经在伊夫堡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 应该已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死人又回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙·唐泰斯忘不了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他绝不会忘记我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里面装着谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这棺材里 到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来打开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不干
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快打开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波毕鲁…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别无选择吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才楼上是不是有什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没注意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概爷爷又从轮椅上衰下来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜睡着的话 就没人去扶他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 说不定还可以当复健
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦蒂埃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.31,0:17:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护瓦朗蒂娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是让我们往这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚 到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 什么态度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得有好事想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克西米利安少爷终于作案了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.97,0:18:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点是维尔福家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:18:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共犯两名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹少爷和勒诺少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也有来找你 但你不在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现三个坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 立即押过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想对小女做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎调查了我不少事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是基督山伯爵的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个都告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比较方便
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.25,0:21:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宅门前好象有骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.56,0:21:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.62,0:21:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即召集部下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋人们离开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的疑惑来临
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突如其来的消息使我迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 岩窟王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.79,0:21:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十一幕\N婚约、决裂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待 然后期待
